description.p:
In view of the above, an object of the present invention is to provide an automatic feeding apparatus for an electric arc furnace, so as to solve the following problems:
I. solving the problem of poor distribution uniformity of stacked steel materials during the conveying process present in the existing feeding apparatus;
II. solving the problem of poor preheating efficiency present in the existing feeding apparatus;
III. solving the problem of poor loading efficiency present in the existing feeding apparatus; and
IV. solving the problem of generating dioxin due to scarp steel heating in the feeding apparatus.
